{
  "esm": "0.8.0",
  "metadata": {
    "name": "advection_1d_ppm_periodic",
    "description": "SELF-CONTAINED regression fixture (earthsci-ast-rs only) for the deep PPM template chain. Byte-equivalent in meaning to EarthSciDiscretizations problems/advection_1d_ppm_periodic.esm with its grids/cartesian_uniform_1d/rules/ppm_D_periodic import chain (rule + ppm_D_interior + ppm_flux + ppm_face_value{,_mono} + ppm_slope{,_mono} + ppm_limit_right + grid) resolved INLINE, so the test needs no sibling repository. MMS driver: 1-D linear advection u_t = -c u_x on the periodic unit interval [0, 1], discretized by grids/cartesian_uniform_1d/rules/ppm_D_periodic (Piecewise Parabolic Method, Colella-Woodward 1984; conservative finite-volume, semi-discrete method-of-lines flux, non-negative speed). Exact solution u(x,t) = sin(2 pi (x - c t)) transported at speed c with no change of shape, so no forcing term is required. FLUX FORM: the rule uses the semi-discrete reconstructed-edge PPM flux F_{i+1/2} = qr_lim(cell i) (the CW84-limited right edge of the upwind cell), not the fully-discrete Courant-integral flux, because the ESS simulate() pathway is method-of-lines (the rule provides only D(u,x); the ODE integrator owns dt) -- see the rule file for the full rationale. OBSERVED ORDER (honest): PPM is nominally 3rd order (parabolic reconstruction) and the unlimited flux-difference is exactly 4th-order central, but the original CW84 monotonicity limiter still clips the two smooth extrema of the sine (the classic smooth-extremum clipping of the 1984 limiter), flattening the parabola there to first order. The global order is therefore sub-nominal and norm-dependent -- about 1.7 in L2 and 1.3 in Linf over N=16..128; the convergence gate (tests/conformance/convergence/advection_1d_ppm_periodic) asserts the honestly-observed order, NOT the nominal 3. CONSERVATION: the flux-difference telescopes on the periodic ring and neighbouring cells share the identical float face flux, so sum(u) (hence mean(u)) is preserved to the bit -- the t=0.1 mean-conservation assertion pins this. The grid's consumer-supplied geometry contract (grids/cartesian_uniform_1d/grid.esm) is fulfilled for [0, 1]: x0 = 0 (parameter) and dx = 1/N (an observed dividing the extent by the metaparameter name N, esm-spec 9.7.6, so the convergence sweep's loader-API rebinding of N keeps dx consistent) resolve the rule body's free dx at evaluation. Initial condition and test references spell the grid's index-to-coordinate conversion x_i = x0 + (i - 1/2) dx = 0 + (i - 1/2)(1/N) inline with load-foldable scalars, not via the free-name x_coord template: the official 6.6.5/ic build-time cellwise evaluation is scope-free (model parameters/observeds are not in scope there).",
    "license": "MIT",
    "tags": [
      "esd:problem",
      "grid:cartesian_uniform_1d",
      "equation:advection",
      "mms"
    ],
    "references": [
      {
        "citation": "Colella, P., & Woodward, P. R. (1984). The Piecewise Parabolic Method (PPM) for gas-dynamical simulations. Journal of Computational Physics, 54(1), 174-201.",
        "doi": "10.1016/0021-9991(84)90143-8"
      },
      {
        "citation": "LeVeque, R. J. (2002). Finite Volume Methods for Hyperbolic Problems. Cambridge University Press. Chapter 6 (high-resolution methods) and Chapter 9 (systems)."
      }
    ]
  },
  "metaparameters": {
    "N": {
      "type": "integer",
      "default": 64,
      "description": "Number of cells along x."
    }
  },
  "index_sets": {
    "x": {
      "kind": "interval",
      "size": "N"
    }
  },
  "models": {
    "AdvectionPPM": {
      "expression_templates": {
        "x_coord": {
          "params": [],
          "description": "Cell-center coordinates x_i = x0 + (i - 1/2) dx, shaped over the x index set. x0 and dx are free names supplied by the consuming model (see metadata.description for the contract).",
          "body": {
            "op": "aggregate",
            "output_idx": [
              "i"
            ],
            "args": [],
            "ranges": {
              "i": {
                "from": "x"
              }
            },
            "expr": {
              "op": "+",
              "args": [
                "x0",
                {
                  "op": "*",
                  "args": [
                    {
                      "op": "-",
                      "args": [
                        "i",
                        0.5
                      ]
                    },
                    "dx"
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "ppm_slope": {
          "params": [
            "am",
            "ap"
          ],
          "description": "CW84 eq.(1.7) uniform-mesh average slope (ap - am)/2",
          "body": {
            "op": "*",
            "args": [
              {
                "op": "/",
                "args": [
                  1,
                  2
                ]
              },
              {
                "op": "-",
                "args": [
                  "ap",
                  "am"
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "ppm_slope_mono": {
          "params": [
            "am",
            "a0",
            "ap"
          ],
          "description": "CW84 eq.(1.8) monotonized slope: 0 at an extremum, else the raw slope clamped to +-2 min(|a0-am|,|ap-a0|)",
          "body": {
            "op": "ifelse",
            "args": [
              {
                "op": ">",
                "args": [
                  {
                    "op": "*",
                    "args": [
                      {
                        "op": "-",
                        "args": [
                          "ap",
                          "a0"
                        ]
                      },
                      {
                        "op": "-",
                        "args": [
                          "a0",
                          "am"
                        ]
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  0
                ]
              },
              {
                "op": "max",
                "args": [
                  {
                    "op": "-",
                    "args": [
                      {
                        "op": "*",
                        "args": [
                          2,
                          {
                            "op": "min",
                            "args": [
                              {
                                "op": "abs",
                                "args": [
                                  {
                                    "op": "-",
                                    "args": [
                                      "a0",
                                      "am"
                                    ]
                                  }
                                ]
                              },
                              {
                                "op": "abs",
                                "args": [
                                  {
                                    "op": "-",
                                    "args": [
                                      "ap",
                                      "a0"
                                    ]
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            ]
                          }
                        ]
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "op": "min",
                    "args": [
                      {
                        "op": "*",
                        "args": [
                          2,
                          {
                            "op": "min",
                            "args": [
                              {
                                "op": "abs",
                                "args": [
                                  {
                                    "op": "-",
                                    "args": [
                                      "a0",
                                      "am"
                                    ]
                                  }
                                ]
                              },
                              {
                                "op": "abs",
                                "args": [
                                  {
                                    "op": "-",
                                    "args": [
                                      "ap",
                                      "a0"
                                    ]
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            ]
                          }
                        ]
                      },
                      {
                        "op": "apply_expression_template",
                        "args": [],
                        "name": "ppm_slope",
                        "bindings": {
                          "am": "am",
                          "ap": "ap"
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              },
              0
            ]
          }
        },
        "ppm_face_value_mono": {
          "params": [
            "a",
            "b",
            "c",
            "d"
          ],
          "description": "face = b + (1/2)(c-b) + (1/6)(slope_mono(a,b,c) - slope_mono(b,c,d))",
          "body": {
            "op": "+",
            "args": [
              "b",
              {
                "op": "*",
                "args": [
                  {
                    "op": "/",
                    "args": [
                      1,
                      2
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "op": "-",
                    "args": [
                      "c",
                      "b"
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "op": "*",
                "args": [
                  {
                    "op": "/",
                    "args": [
                      1,
                      6
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "op": "-",
                    "args": [
                      {
                        "op": "apply_expression_template",
                        "args": [],
                        "name": "ppm_slope_mono",
                        "bindings": {
                          "am": "a",
                          "a0": "b",
                          "ap": "c"
                        }
